window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>At a top secret research laboratory in Nevada, DARPA's most advanced artificial intelligence can read your darkest secrets and hidden intentions right off your face. </p> <p>The technology's manipulative inventor, however, fears no future big brother surveillance state. He built it for his own secret reasons - and now there is no untruth he won't tell, no subterfuge he won't pull, to help his estranged young daughter. </p> <p>To protect his troubled little girl, Trevor Lennox will change our world. He will give Amy what no one else can: a world without lies. But there are some secrets that should stay buried forever...When the base around him erupts in murder and mayhem, Trevor himself must face the horrifying truth. </p> <p>The lies we tell ourselves can be the deadliest of all.... </p>"; 
